<h1>Free Sprite Sheet Packer</h1>
<p>
This tool is a <b>free online alternative</b> for <a href="/texturepacker">TexturePacker</a>. You can use it to pack sprite sheets,
including data formats for Phaser, CSS and LESS. <br />
</p>
<p>
Simply drag &amp; drop your sprites into the main area and download the created .png files.
<b>Privacy notice</b>: No data is transferred to our servers &mdash; the sprites are packed in your browser.
</p>
